  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Immersive Visuals</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2109840/extras/d8794ac3ef058d6d73638c7762cf1b43.poster.avif?t=1750948772\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2109840/extras/d8794ac3ef058d6d73638c7762cf1b43.webm?t=1750948772\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experience ancient China in a visually stunning, realistic side-scrolling 3D action-adventure. Play as a master swordswoman, a deadly assassin fighting for justice.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Engaging Gameplay</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2109840/extras/5088b1027cc20dbff2f1f09a4116f76e.poster.avif?t=1750948772\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2109840/extras/5088b1027cc20dbff2f1f09a4116f76e.webm?t=1750948772\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Engage in thrilling stealth and combat. Infiltrate heavily guarded palaces to eliminate key targets, using stealth or brute force to overcome obstacles.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2109840/extras/1ac0a3d6ecfac1db20b7590ce67b04eb.poster.avif?t=1750948772\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2109840/extras/1ac0a3d6ecfac1db20b7590ce67b04eb.webm?t=1750948772\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Engage in dynamic sword fights, showcasing your mastery of combat.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2109840/extras/1ff72752b544842d518dd65c4d647aa8.poster.avif?t=1750948772\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2109840/extras/1ff72752b544842d518dd65c4d647aa8.webm?t=1750948772\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore diverse environments, from misty mountain forests to tranquil temples, each filled with danger.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Varied Environments</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2109840/extras/2fe2967529d1eb06415b307ec1412f84.poster.avif?t=1750948772\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2109840/extras/2fe2967529d1eb06415b307ec1412f84.webm?t=1750948772\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Journey through vast deserts, barren landscapes, and treacherous canyons. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2109840/extras/1adf74b95215eda7bdd38eae24d021d5.poster.avif?t=1750948772\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2109840/extras/1adf74b95215eda7bdd38eae24d021d5.webm?t=1750948772\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore intricate indoor levels with fluid parkour mechanics.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2109840/extras/6ef9cd91aacbd209de95e47cc3db632e.poster.avif?t=1750948772\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2109840/extras/6ef9cd91aacbd209de95e47cc3db632e.webm?t=1750948772\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2109840/extras/9586f4d629d3997c0db407c7a3db6eb0.poster.avif?t=1750948772\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2109840/extras/9586f4d629d3997c0db407c7a3db6eb0.webm?t=1750948772\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Navigate deadly traps and hidden passages, requiring both skill and cunning.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Breathtaking </strong>BOSS battle</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2109840/extras/90221c3673fd298ee68a82a23643277e.poster.avif?t=1750948772\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2109840/extras/90221c3673fd298ee68a82a23643277e.webm?t=1750948772\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2109840/extras/1ac0a3d6ecfac1db20b7590ce67b04eb.poster.avif?t=1750948772\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2109840/extras/1ac0a3d6ecfac1db20b7590ce67b04eb.webm?t=1750948772\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2109840/extras/617d3be05e3189e9d63015ccb5f5493c.poster.avif?t=1750948772\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2109840/extras/617d3be05e3189e9d63015ccb5f5493c.webm?t=1750948772\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2109840/extras/b3aa7f696917c2d16761ffedf4bd0422.poster.avif?t=1750948772\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2109840/extras/b3aa7f696917c2d16761ffedf4bd0422.webm?t=1750948772\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2109840/extras/838ea2854040c44ede2e3bf8f4cf98ba.poster.avif?t=1750948772\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/app