  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Immersive Visuals</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2109840/extras/d8794ac3ef058d6d73638c7762cf1b43.poster.avif?t=1750948772\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2109840/extras/d8794ac3ef058d6d73638c7762cf1b43.webm?t=1750948772\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experience ancient China in a visually stunning, realistic side-scrolling 3D action-adventure. Play as a master swordswoman, a deadly assassin fighting for justice.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Engaging Gameplay</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2109840/extras/5088b1027cc20dbff2f1f09a4116f76e.poster.avif?t=1750948772\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2109840/extras/5088b1027cc20dbff2f1f09a4116f76e.webm?t=1750948772\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Engage in thrilling stealth and combat. Infiltrate heavily guarded palaces to eliminate key targets, using stealth or brute force to overcome obstacles.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2109840/extras/1ac0a3d6ecfac1db20b7590ce67b04eb.poster.avif?t=1750948772\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://share